==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pardonable
<hw>Par"don*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>pardonnable</ets>.]</ety> <def>Admitting of pardon; not requiring
the excution of penalty; venial; excusable; -- applied to the offense or
to the offender; <as>as, a <ex>pardonable</ex> fault, or
culprit</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pardonableness</ent>⟦br⟧
